<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200918/8f80c84df7024105b3db761ef4354e98.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲方坤·国画作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200918/d4c8c8625d4b48d89a863ba0a06fdb8d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲方坤·国画作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200918/d9768cbfce904d9cba1494f1eb221ced.png" max-width="600" /></p>
